cs.CR, cs.CY, cs.DL, cs.SI, cs.DB

This paper is primarily focused on the analysis of ransomware payments in the Bitcoin ecosystem, which is a topic related to cybersecurity (cs.CR) and cybercrime (cs.CY). The paper also involves the use of data-driven methods and analysis (cs.DL) and the application of machine learning techniques (cs.SI) to identify and gather information on Bitcoin transactions. Additionally, the paper utilizes a platform for analyzing blockchain data (cs.DB).
